*Jump Shop (2005) – designed ''Weekly Shōnen Jump'''s online shop's {{nihongo|Janta|ジャンタ}} character
*"[[Rule/Sparkle]]" ([[Ayumi Hamasaki]] single, 2006) – an illustration of Ayumi Hamasaki as Son Goku printed on the single's CD and DVD
*''[[Weekly Shōnen Jump]]'' (2009) – designed the magazine's website's {{nihongo|Kaizo-kun|KAIZOくん}} character
*''Invade'' ([[Jealkb]] album, 2011) – album cover

